title: Vegans Kill Cockroaches (Vivisection, Agriculture & Activism)
description: Well… the title itself is long enough to serve as the description: the video offers some real talk on vivisection, agriculture and activism, with challenging contrasts between idealism and pragmatism, as (hopefully) veganism becomes a crucial part of ecology in the 21st century.
